AngloGold Ashanti ‘On Track’ to Meet Its First-Quarter Production Guidance

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-03T11:01:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/anglogold-ashanti-on-track-to-meet-its-first-quarter-production-guidance.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG)  said first-
quarter production “remains on track” to meet the company’s
guidance of 1.039 million ounces.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
